author: Honest Astrologer
text: Your rising sign or ascendant zodiac changes every two hours a day too. It cannot be fixed like some people claim it to be. You can't expect planets to exhibit static motion.

author: Honest Astrologer
text:
The biggest misconception is that a particular month will give you a particular zodiac people. 

This is far from the truth. 
 
☀️ and 🌙 are continuously moving and whichever sign they will be in at the time of your birth is your ☀️ and 🌙 sign respectively.
